Enables creation and management of standardized schedule patterns that can be reused across multiple schedule periods.
Critical for maintaining consistency in scheduling practices while reducing time and effort required to create new schedules.
Templates capture proven scheduling approaches that meet business requirements and compliance constraints. Supports versioning
