and compliance reporting. Supports hierarchical location structures allowing parent-child relationships between
locations. Timezone field critical for scheduling across geographic regions ensuring accurate shift timing and
compliance with local labor laws. Comprehensive address structure enables geocoding for route optimization,
delivery planning, and proximity searches. Location type categorization allows type-specific business rules
and reporting. Tracks operational status supporting location closures, renovations, or seasonal operations
without losing historical data. Essential for multi-entity operations enabling proper segregation of data
and operations by location while maintaining single source of truth. Hierarchical structure supports
organizational roll-ups for reporting, budgeting, and strategic planning. Metadata JSONB field provides
flexibility for location-specific attributes without schema modifications.';

