COMMENT ON TABLE integration.webhooks IS 'Configuration for webhook integrations with external systems.
Manages configuration of webhook integrations that enable real-time data synchronization with external systems. Stores
endpoint URLs, authentication details, and event subscriptions for each integration. Critical for implementing event-driven
architecture that responds to scheduling changes without requiring polling. Supports multiple authentication methods including
API keys, OAuth, and mutual TLS. Includes retry policies and error handling rules to ensure reliable delivery. Tracks delivery
statistics and error rates for monitoring and troubleshooting. Includes filtering capabilities to reduce unnecessary traffic.
Supports both system-defined and user-defined webhooks for flexibility. Maintains historical configuration data for auditing.
Centralizes webhook management for consistent security practices. Optimized for rapid lookup during event processing to minimize
latency in webhook delivery.';


