    values; CONSISTENCY: Uniformity of data across systems and over time; TIMELINESS: Availability of data within required
    timeframes; VALIDITY: Conformance to defined business rules and formats; UNIQUENESS: Absence of duplicate records;
    INTEGRITY: Referential integrity and relationship consistency; DUPlication_RATE: Rate of duplicate records;
    FORMAT_COMPLIANCE: Adherence to defined data formats; RANGE_COMPLIANCE: Values within expected ranges;
    REFERENCE_INTEGRITY: Validity of reference data relationships; BUSINESS_RULE_COMPLIANCE: Adherence to specific business rules.';

