        -- Serial No: 86 | TABLE: finance.payroll_records
        -- Description: Payroll calculation and processing records
        -- Business Case: The payroll_records table stores detailed payroll calculation data, providing a
        -- transparent and auditable record of all compensation calculations for employees. It captures
        -- regular hours, overtime, bonuses, deductions, and other payroll elements with supporting
        -- documentation for each calculation. The table supports multiple pay frequencies and
        -- compensation structures, accommodating different employment types and contractual arrangements.
        -- Each payroll record includes metadata about the calculation rules applied, tax jurisdictions,
