                minimum requirements and stretch goals. Includes metadata about effective dates and priority. Accommodates complex benchmark
                scenarios such as conditional benchmarks. Benchmark data versioned to track changes over time. Optimized for rapid querying
                during performance evaluation. Historical data used to identify patterns and improve goal-setting. Tracks approval status for
                compliance purposes. Centralizes benchmark configuration for effective communication about performance expectations. Optimized
                for rapid querying during performance evaluation.';



