                -- retention period to meet regulatory requirements and support trend analysis. For performance reasons,
                -- the system implements differential storage of changes rather than full copies of schedules, optimizing
                -- storage efficiency while maintaining complete historical information. The table also tracks the
                -- business rationale for significant changes to support audit inquiries and process improvement
                -- initiatives. By centralizing schedule history, the organization can ensure consistent tracking of
