                    -- collection through scheduled jobs, ensuring timely assessment of system health. For metrics with
                    -- defined targets, the table stores variance calculations to highlight areas requiring attention.
                    -- Historical metric data is used to establish baselines and detect anomalies that may indicate
                    -- underlying system issues. By centralizing system health metrics, the organization can ensure
                    -- comprehensive monitoring that provides visibility into system performance across all components.
