'Business rules that guide the staffing optimization engine to balance coverage, cost, compliance, and preferences. 
Encodes business constraints, optimization priorities, and operational preferences into the scheduling algorithm.';

COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.staffing_optimization_rules.rule_id IS 'Unique identifier for the optimization rule';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.staffing_optimization_rules.rule_code IS 'Business-readable rule code (format: RUL-XXX-YYYYYY)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.staffing_optimization_rules.rule_expression IS 'SQL or custom expression defining the rule logic';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.staffing_optimization_rules.weight IS 'Weight factor for optimization scoring (higher = more important)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.staffing_optimization_rules.rule_parameters IS 'JSON object containing rule-specific configuration parameters';
