'Multi-level schedule approval workflow tracking. Manages complex approval workflows 
for schedule publication, ensuring appropriate review and authorization at each level. 
Supports configurable approval hierarchies, delegation rules, and escalation procedures. 
Provides audit trails for all approval decisions and enables compliance with internal controls.';

COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.approval_id IS 'Unique identifier for the approval record (UUID)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.approval_code IS 'Business-readable approval code (format: APR-SCHD-XXXXXX)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.schedule_id IS 'Reference to the schedule being approved';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.approver_id IS 'Employee ID of the approver';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.approver_role IS 'Organizational role of the approver (MANAGER, DIRECTOR, VP, etc.)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.approval_level IS 'Level in approval hierarchy (1-10)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.approval_chain_position IS 'Position in the approval chain sequence';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.status IS 'Current approval status (PENDING, APPROVED, REJECTED, etc.)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.response_time IS 'Calculated time taken to respond to approval request (auto-generated)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.is_delegated IS 'Indicates if approval was delegated to another approver';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.is_escalated IS 'Indicates if approval was escalated to higher authority';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.is_final_approval IS 'Indicates if this is the final approval in the chain';
COMMENT ON COLUMN scheduling.schedule_approvals.workflow_instance_id IS 'Reference to workflow instance for tracking';
